{{vgname2|山姆·奥斯卡·兰迪加|en=Sam Oscar Lantinga}}，曾是[[暴雪娱乐|暴雪娱乐]]的软件工程师，目前在[[Valve|Valve]]软件公司工作<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://lists.libsdl.org/pipermail/sdl-libsdl.org/2012-July/085112.html |title=Sam Lantinga at Valve Software |accessdate=2015-09-02 |archive-date=2013-05-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130515202909/http://lists.libsdl.org/pipermail/sdl-libsdl.org/2012-July/085112.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，因为创立DirectMedia Layer而知名<ref name="ardicredit">[http://www.ardi.com/website.php ARDI site credits] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070609200206/http://www.ardi.com/website.php |date=2007-06-09 }}</ref>。

此前，他是洛基软件的主程序员和联合创始人之一<ref>[http://www.phoronix.com/scan.php?page=news_item&px=OTA0NQ Blizzard Still Has a World of Warcraft Linux Client] {{Wayback|url=http://www.phoronix.com/scan.php?page=news_item&px=OTA0NQ |date=20150924130907 }} [[Phoronix|Phoronix]], January 25, 2011 (Article by [[Michael_Larabel|Michael Larabel]])</ref><ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20050712080821/http://www.linuxgazette.com/node/10249 "Linux Game Publishing: An Interview With Michael Simms" Linux Gazette (2005-06-03)]</ref>。2008年，他创立了Galaxy Gameworks<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.galaxygameworks.com/about.html |title=About Galaxy Gameworks |accessdate=2015-09-02 |archive-date=2015-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150906025243/http://www.galaxygameworks.com/about.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，之后离开暴雪娱乐<ref>[http://forums.libsdl.org/viewtopic.php?t=6804 Simple DirectMedia Layer Forums] {{Wayback|url=http://forums.libsdl.org/viewtopic.php?t=6804 |date=20160303222315 }}, retrieved on 2011-01-06</ref>。不久，他推出创立新网站Gameworks。<ref>[http://www.linuxgames.com/archives/16631 Galaxy Gameworks] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110310160438/http://www.linuxgames.com/archives/16631 |date=2011-03-10 }} [[LinuxGames|LinuxGames]], March 6, 2011 (Article by "Crusader")</ref> 并在38工作室中工作，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.linkedin.com/pub/sam-lantinga/10/71b/27 |title=Sam Lantinga at LinkedIn |accessdate=2015-09-02 |archive-date=2010-07-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100705125509/http://www.linkedin.com/pub/sam-lantinga/10/71b/27 |dead-url=no }}</ref>直到这家公司在2012年5月关闭。

